{"title":"Node安装及更换源","slug":"杂七腊八/环境配置/node环境安装","date":"2020-09-28T11:23:03.000Z","updated":"2022-02-21T04:45:27.404Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/杂七腊八/环境配置/node环境安装.json","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/9376e116711dd.png","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/7ebe76d36f15d.png","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/3ce8efc8c9b2c.png","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/3783363276438.png","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/ab0e545f77013.png","https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/832afe33ly1g9jo1d2ta0j20ug0gumy6.jpg","https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/832afe33ly1g9jo38c017j20in0gw750.jpg","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/7deec41f1ab42.png","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/4ff595aa4bd1d.png","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/dee009e26620d.png","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/8efcad9b1fc57.png","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/de4a7bb431821.png","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/cfe1f3e1293ee.png","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/e78732a80fc21.png","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/8606c336336f4.png","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/ae9b304f8d861.png","https://rmt.ladydaily.com/fetch/tzk/storage/.png?w=1280&amp;fmt=jpg","https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/e4d3c84f6c09b.png"],"content":"<h2 id=\"nodejs的安装\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#nodejs的安装\"></a> NodeJs的安装</h2>\n<p>无论是何种系统进行安装，都需要到其<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/\">官网</a>进行下载。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/9376e116711dd.png\" alt=\"image-20200928171937938\" /></p>\n<h3 id=\"windows\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#windows\"></a> Windows</h3>\n<p>Windows版本以Windows10 64位为例，为了方便我选择msi安装方式进行安装。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>下载</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/7ebe76d36f15d.png\" alt=\"image-20200928172703010\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装步骤</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>选择安装位置</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/3ce8efc8c9b2c.png\" alt=\"image-20200928173312063\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>下一步</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/3783363276438.png\" alt=\"image-20200928173338162\" /></p>\n<p>接下来一路下一步即可。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>验证是否安装成功</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/ab0e545f77013.png\" alt=\"image-20200928181405646\" /></p>\n<p>终端内输入命令<code>node -v</code>即可验证node是否安装成功。输入<code>npm -v</code>即可验证npm是否安装成功。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"linux\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#linux\"></a> Linux</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>下载安装包</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/832afe33ly1g9jo1d2ta0j20ug0gumy6.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>如果是服务器，那么上传到服务器。如果是本地，那么直接解压即可。</p>\n<p>解压命令参考<code>tar -xvf 文件名</code>。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>切换用户，切换用户到root用户，并将解压出来的文件夹移动。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">mv</span> node /usr/local/src/<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>变基环境变量<br />\n<code>vi /etc/profile</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">NODE_HOME</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/usr/local/src/node\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\">$NODE_HOME</span>/bin:<span class=\"token environment constant\">$PATH</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/832afe33ly1g9jo38c017j20in0gw750.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>运行命令<code>source /etc/profile</code>使配置生效</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"多版本管理\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#多版本管理\"></a> 多版本管理</h2>\n<p>对于node的多版本管理推荐使用nvm。其GitHub开源（Windows）地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/coreybutler/nvm-windows/releases\">https://github.com/coreybutler/nvm-windows/releases</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/7deec41f1ab42.png\" alt=\"image-20200928183305331\" /></p>\n<p>为了方便起见推荐使用安装版本。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>双击安装二进制文件进行安装</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>管理问题</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/4ff595aa4bd1d.png\" alt=\"image-20200928183437109\" /></p>\n<p>上面的原因是：nvm检测到已经安装了node12.18.4版本，正在询问是否使用nvm对这个版本进行管理。选择<strong>是</strong>即可。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装完成</p>\n<p>安装完成后，打开命令行输入<code>nvm v</code>即可看到安装的版本。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/dee009e26620d.png\" alt=\"image-20200928183628717\" /></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"换源\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#换源\"></a> 换源</h2>\n<p>npm默认使用的是官方源，在国内使用非常不便。为了便于国内开发者下载包，有热心的开发者提供了nrm，即对npm源管理的工具。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>通过<code>npm install -g nrm</code>进行全局安装。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/8efcad9b1fc57.png\" alt=\"image-20200928185057491\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>查看当前源</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">nrm <span class=\"token function\">ls</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/de4a7bb431821.png\" alt=\"image-20200928185152287\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>使用淘宝源</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">nrm use taobao<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/cfe1f3e1293ee.png\" alt=\"image-20200928185225571\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>其他使用</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/e78732a80fc21.png\" alt=\"image-20200928185517613\" /></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"npm的替代工具yarn\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#npm的替代工具yarn\"></a> NPM的替代工具YARN</h2>\n<p>简单来说，Yarn 是为了弥补 npm 的一些缺陷而出现的。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>安装</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -g <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/8606c336336f4.png\" alt=\"image-20200928185930302\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>验证版本</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> -v<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/ae9b304f8d861.png\" alt=\"image-20200928190007147\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>使用介绍</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"></th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">NPM</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">YARN</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">初始化</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm init</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn init</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">默认安装依赖</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm install</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn install</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">安装某个依赖并保存</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm install xxxx -save</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn add xxxx</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">安装全局依赖</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm install -g xxxx</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn global add xxxx</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">移除依赖</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm uninstall xxxx -save</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn remove xxxx</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">更新依赖</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm update</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn upgrade xxxx</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">运行指令</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm run</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn run</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"关于yarn全局安装\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#关于yarn全局安装\"></a> 关于yarn全局安装</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>修改全局安装目录, 先创建好目录。例如我的目录<code>F:\\coding\\nvm\\yarn</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> config <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> prefix F:<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>coding<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>nvm<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>yarn<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>修改全局安装目录的bin目录位置, bin目录需要自己创建或者全局安装一个插件后自己会生成。为了能全局使用安装出的命令，还需要将其（bin目录）加入环境变量</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> config <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> prefix <span class=\"token string\">\"F:<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\c\">\\c</span>oding<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\n\">\\n</span>vm\\yarn\"</span>\t<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>修改全局缓存目录, 先创建好目录(cache), 和global放在同一层目录下</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> config <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> cache-folder F:<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>coding<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>nvm<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>yarn<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>cache<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://rmt.ladydaily.com/fetch/tzk/storage/.png?w=1280&amp;fmt=jpg\" alt=\"image-20201024111358451\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>全局安装</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> global <span class=\"token function\">add</span> xxx<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"源管理\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#源管理\"></a> 源管理</h3>\n<p>yarn也有类似的工具，即yrm。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -g yrm<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/e4d3c84f6c09b.png\" alt=\"image-20200928190956058\" /></p>\n<p>使用方式与nrm类似。</p>\n","more":"<h2 id=\"nodejs的安装\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#nodejs的安装\"></a> NodeJs的安装</h2>\n<p>无论是何种系统进行安装，都需要到其<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/\">官网</a>进行下载。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/9376e116711dd.png\" alt=\"image-20200928171937938\" /></p>\n<h3 id=\"windows\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#windows\"></a> Windows</h3>\n<p>Windows版本以Windows10 64位为例，为了方便我选择msi安装方式进行安装。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>下载</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/7ebe76d36f15d.png\" alt=\"image-20200928172703010\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装步骤</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>选择安装位置</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/3ce8efc8c9b2c.png\" alt=\"image-20200928173312063\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>下一步</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/3783363276438.png\" alt=\"image-20200928173338162\" /></p>\n<p>接下来一路下一步即可。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>验证是否安装成功</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/ab0e545f77013.png\" alt=\"image-20200928181405646\" /></p>\n<p>终端内输入命令<code>node -v</code>即可验证node是否安装成功。输入<code>npm -v</code>即可验证npm是否安装成功。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"linux\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#linux\"></a> Linux</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>下载安装包</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/832afe33ly1g9jo1d2ta0j20ug0gumy6.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>如果是服务器，那么上传到服务器。如果是本地，那么直接解压即可。</p>\n<p>解压命令参考<code>tar -xvf 文件名</code>。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>切换用户，切换用户到root用户，并将解压出来的文件夹移动。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">mv</span> node /usr/local/src/<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>变基环境变量<br />\n<code>vi /etc/profile</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">NODE_HOME</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/usr/local/src/node\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token variable\">$NODE_HOME</span>/bin:<span class=\"token environment constant\">$PATH</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/832afe33ly1g9jo38c017j20in0gw750.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>运行命令<code>source /etc/profile</code>使配置生效</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"多版本管理\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#多版本管理\"></a> 多版本管理</h2>\n<p>对于node的多版本管理推荐使用nvm。其GitHub开源（Windows）地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/coreybutler/nvm-windows/releases\">https://github.com/coreybutler/nvm-windows/releases</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/7deec41f1ab42.png\" alt=\"image-20200928183305331\" /></p>\n<p>为了方便起见推荐使用安装版本。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>双击安装二进制文件进行安装</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>管理问题</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/4ff595aa4bd1d.png\" alt=\"image-20200928183437109\" /></p>\n<p>上面的原因是：nvm检测到已经安装了node12.18.4版本，正在询问是否使用nvm对这个版本进行管理。选择<strong>是</strong>即可。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装完成</p>\n<p>安装完成后，打开命令行输入<code>nvm v</code>即可看到安装的版本。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/dee009e26620d.png\" alt=\"image-20200928183628717\" /></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"换源\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#换源\"></a> 换源</h2>\n<p>npm默认使用的是官方源，在国内使用非常不便。为了便于国内开发者下载包，有热心的开发者提供了nrm，即对npm源管理的工具。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>通过<code>npm install -g nrm</code>进行全局安装。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/8efcad9b1fc57.png\" alt=\"image-20200928185057491\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>查看当前源</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">nrm <span class=\"token function\">ls</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/de4a7bb431821.png\" alt=\"image-20200928185152287\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>使用淘宝源</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">nrm use taobao<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/cfe1f3e1293ee.png\" alt=\"image-20200928185225571\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>其他使用</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/e78732a80fc21.png\" alt=\"image-20200928185517613\" /></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"npm的替代工具yarn\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#npm的替代工具yarn\"></a> NPM的替代工具YARN</h2>\n<p>简单来说，Yarn 是为了弥补 npm 的一些缺陷而出现的。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>安装</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -g <span class=\"token function\">yarn</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/8606c336336f4.png\" alt=\"image-20200928185930302\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>验证版本</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> -v<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/ae9b304f8d861.png\" alt=\"image-20200928190007147\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>使用介绍</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\"></th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">NPM</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">YARN</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">初始化</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm init</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn init</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">默认安装依赖</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm install</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn install</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">安装某个依赖并保存</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm install xxxx -save</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn add xxxx</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">安装全局依赖</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm install -g xxxx</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn global add xxxx</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">移除依赖</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm uninstall xxxx -save</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn remove xxxx</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">更新依赖</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm update</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn upgrade xxxx</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">运行指令</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>npm run</code></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"><code>yarn run</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"关于yarn全局安装\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#关于yarn全局安装\"></a> 关于yarn全局安装</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>修改全局安装目录, 先创建好目录。例如我的目录<code>F:\\coding\\nvm\\yarn</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> config <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> prefix F:<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>coding<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>nvm<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>yarn<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>修改全局安装目录的bin目录位置, bin目录需要自己创建或者全局安装一个插件后自己会生成。为了能全局使用安装出的命令，还需要将其（bin目录）加入环境变量</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> config <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> prefix <span class=\"token string\">\"F:<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\c\">\\c</span>oding<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\n\">\\n</span>vm\\yarn\"</span>\t<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>修改全局缓存目录, 先创建好目录(cache), 和global放在同一层目录下</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> config <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> cache-folder F:<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>coding<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>nvm<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>yarn<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>cache<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://rmt.ladydaily.com/fetch/tzk/storage/.png?w=1280&amp;fmt=jpg\" alt=\"image-20201024111358451\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>全局安装</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">yarn</span> global <span class=\"token function\">add</span> xxx<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"源管理\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#源管理\"></a> 源管理</h3>\n<p>yarn也有类似的工具，即yrm。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -g yrm<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://files.alexhchu.com/2020/09/28/e4d3c84f6c09b.png\" alt=\"image-20200928190956058\" /></p>\n<p>使用方式与nrm类似。</p>\n","categories":[{"name":"大前端","path":"api/categories/大前端.json"},{"name":"NodeJs","path":"api/categories/NodeJs.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"NodeJs","path":"api/tags/NodeJs.json"}]}